<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="exp" id="exp">exp</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Składnia:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">double</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

Funkcja exp() zwraca <em>e</em> (~2.7182818) podniesione do potęgi <em>num</em>.
</p>

<p>
C++ dostarcza również przeciążone wersje funkcji: 

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">float</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>  <span class="co1">//to samo co expf() w C99</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">exp</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> num<span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span>  <span class="co1">//to samo co expl() w C99</span></pre>
<p>
Tematy pokrewne: <a href="log" class="wikilink1" title="pl:numeric:c:log">log</a>, <a href="pow" class="wikilink1" title="pl:numeric:c:pow">pow</a>, <a href="sqrt" class="wikilink1" title="pl:numeric:c:sqrt">sqrt</a>
</p>

